Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.61,0:01:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 維多利加 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.45,0:01:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圖書館裏應該有什麽 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.74,0:01:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 當然是書 對吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.33,0:01:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個少女啊 為了藏葉于林 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.24,0:02:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才來這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.17,0:02:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女撿到書的時候 發覺被你看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.32,0:02:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想到要藏起來 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.53,0:02:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話 圖書館是最合適的 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.92,0:02:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那本書是什麽 想知道吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.11,0:02:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 怎麽找呢 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.31,0:02:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道 通往天國的第十三層階梯 的怪談吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.27,0:02:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那停下腳步的話就會被帶到天國去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.93,0:02:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個書架裏面收藏著古今東西的宗教書籍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.07,0:02:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 這裡就是 天國的書架 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.06,0:02:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.04,0:02:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2 3 4 5 6 7 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.18,0:02:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.58,0:02:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8 9 10 11 12 13 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.38,0:03:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就是 通往天國的第十三層階梯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.77,0:03:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡停下的人就遭殃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.00,0:03:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女把書藏到了這個書架裏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.91,0:03:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智慧之泉這麽告訴我的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.55,0:03:20.36,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第5話 廢棄倉庫裏的謎之幽靈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.45,0:03:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又乾淨俐落地解開了一個謎啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.79,0:03:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金色妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.52,0:03:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灰色之狼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.25,0:03:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可思議的維多利加 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.79,0:03:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在高塔中的金色妖精 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.30,0:03:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金色妖精 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.67,0:03:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 翻太快了啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.92,0:03:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.98,0:03:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹什麽啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.65,0:03:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的頭太礙事了 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.97,0:03:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不打算讓我一起看嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.44,0:03:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.69,0:04:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.20,0:04:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是一個遙遠的國度的傳說 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.07,0:04:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在森林深處矗立著一座高塔 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.43,0:04:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡住著一個 金色妖精 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.89,0:04:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她知道這世界上所有的謎團 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.37,0:04:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給迷惘的人指出明路 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.10,0:04:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 作為交換要奪走對方的靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.36,0:04:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後吃掉它 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.99,0:04:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得很像維多利加 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.28,0:04:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 圖書館的金色妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.48,0:04:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指的維多利加吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.09,0:04:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽了 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.24,0:04:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明信片啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.15,0:04:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾薇兒·布萊德利 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.05,0:04:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是給艾薇兒的信啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.97,0:04:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫信的人是 布萊德利卿 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.12,0:04:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾薇兒的爺爺啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.26,0:04:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郵票上沒有郵戳啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.87,0:04:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 這封信還沒有交給過艾薇兒 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.03,0:05:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.98,0:05:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我膩了 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.63,0:05:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的事情也解決了吧 給我快回去 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.20,0:05:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然膩了 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.37,0:05:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 維多利加 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.71,0:05:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在想什麽啊 維多利加她 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.60,0:05:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為我們能好好相處的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.43,0:05:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官 怎麽了 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.70,0:05:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,案子的謎不是解開了嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.10,0:05:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那樣的啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.91,0:05:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騎士木乃伊事件剛結束 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.44,0:05:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次又有消息說怪盜潛入村子了 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.59,0:05:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們正在調查呢 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.84,0:05:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字是 怪盜奎亞那 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.82,0:05:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在歐洲橫行的大盜 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.29,0:06:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今為止已經七八年沒有消息了 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.70,0:06:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隱退了 還是死了的傳說都有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.81,0:06:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近有消息說 第二代出現了 而且盯上這個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.88,0:06:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 警官 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.53,0:06:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得 你和平時不一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.89,0:06:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加在的時候 會更加的夸張 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.38,0:06:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.55,0:06:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 男孩喲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.63,0:06:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說些什麽啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.90,0:06:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 看到奇怪的人 要馬上報告啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.33,0:06:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.67,0:06:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.38,0:06:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都什麽跟什麽啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.57,0:07:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.00,0:07:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒過來了嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.45,0:07:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.73,0:07:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 沒事 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.23,0:07:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 久城 倒在倉庫的邊上 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.55,0:07:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我發現你了 把你運到這的 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.12,0:07:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 謝謝你 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.42,0:07:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書沒了 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.31,0:07:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽了 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.02,0:07:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麽 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.66,0:07:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.30,0:07:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個倉庫 說是有女孩子的幽靈會出現 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.23,0:07:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人敢接近那 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.29,0:07:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城 你不是被幽靈襲擊了吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.66,0:07:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.18,0:07:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是 艾薇兒襲擊的我 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.85,0:08:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是個怪談很多的學院呢 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.71,0:08:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.84,0:08:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會是那樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.25,0:08:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 把那書藏起來的是艾薇兒 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.37,0:08:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.36,0:08:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圖書館也有呢 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.16,0:08:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像叫 金色妖精 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.98,0:08:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個妖精十分聰明 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.91,0:08:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽問題都能解決 但是作為交換 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.47,0:08:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要占有人類的靈魂 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.26,0:08:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得 與其說是妖精 更像是惡魔呢 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.58,0:08:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.94,0:08:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圖書館最上面那個是 維多利加 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.87,0:08:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.32,0:08:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是逃課 去那裡一個人看書的 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.85,0:08:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圖書館裏那個 不是金色妖精 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.13,0:08:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是金發的小女孩兒 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.30,0:08:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要的回報不是靈魂 而是點心 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.27,0:08:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 據說那個孩子誰都沒有見過的 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.70,0:08:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的存在嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.62,0:08:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的 維多利加真的存在 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.85,0:08:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 這樣啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.66,0:09:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.13,0:09:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.65,0:09:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書 沒有啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.21,0:09:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 久城 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.56,0:09:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 已經不要緊了嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.20,0:09:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 昨天謝謝你啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.06,0:09:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 比起那個 你聽說了嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.81,0:09:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個干尸 是這學校畢業生 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.61,0:09:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好恐怖啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 一想起來又
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.47,0:09:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.19,0:09:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.20,0:09:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這書是哪來的啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.50,0:09:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 哦 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.25,0:09:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被丟在花壇後面的 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.74,0:09:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丟在那裡
