Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.68,0:10:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒了 剛剛明明在那兒的 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.02,0:10:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾薇兒 
